snippet.title: Xion Leak - 3rd trailer (demo 2024)
snippet.description:
⚡ Demo available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1948490/Xion_Leak/
👉 Wishlist it now!!

Cooperate quickly as a duo and win trophies! 🏆
Escape before the Xion gas fries your precious circuits!

Show what a crack team you are by solving the puzzles created by the mysterious Foreman. 😈
